title: r/Entitledparents "I Like Your Infant More, So Let's Trade Babies!"
description:
r/Entitledparents In today's story, OP's aunt is an insane entitled woman who care about her social standing more than anything else. So when OP's aunt sees that a family member gave birth to a more beautiful child (in her opinion), the aunt actually tries to trade babies! She argues that she deserves the prettier baby because their family is richer, so they can give the child a better life. If you like this podcast and want to see more, hit the follow button.

Watch on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kw5jsD84IG8
